In the Matter of OCEAN TOWNSHIP BOARD OF EDUCATION, Petitioner,
v.
WARETOWN EDUCATION ASSOCIATION, Respondent. C-609 September Term 2018
081833 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 8, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003457-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
